            <h6 style="text-align:justify; margin:20px">Environmental pollution is one of today's urgent problems, it threatens biodiversity, climate change and many other systems that humans must endure. Educating people to be conscious of environmental protection is a solution to protect the environment for the future. Especially for plastic waste, with its sustainable nature, plastic waste (plastic bottles, plastic bags, cotton food boxes, cups...) along with other environmental pollutants has had and is having a negative impact on the environment and human health worldwide.</h6>
